active SECRET security clearance.  Work Location:  Work is performed on government site at the Mark Center, unless directed. Employees will work in close proximity with Government personnel. Core work hours are 0800 to 1700 Monday through Friday except holidays.   Check out our -1192794121to learn more about us!      Recommended skills  Data Analysis  Data Mining  Data Quality  Data Management  Business Intelligence  Data Governance  "}
